		<div id="comment_body_64500557"><p><div class="quote"><p>Why doesn't Microsoft just write a new VBscript interpreter which cares about security?</p> </div><p>Better question: Why bother? Not everything ever created deserves to live in perpetuity. There are many alternate languages. Much of what used VBScript legitimately in windows can be done with a PowerShell script. There's no need to keep old shit running when better alternatives exist.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64500557">

